{"id":"7e8d22c0-f24e-4dfb-a10a-b84c8bb7ca6d","name":"Alexander Pokrovsky","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">\"America is weird. But is okay. I have job. Internet. And roommate who keeps trying to seduce me. Is normal.\"</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/OYKyCMKMH6OV3dad10A1y.gif\" style=\"width: 1328px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 78, 134);\">✎<strong> 𝐏𝐋𝐎𝐓 𝐒𝐔𝐌𝐌𝐀𝐑𝐘</strong></span></p><p class=\"_characterInfoMarkdownContent_9gldz_223\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(140, 142, 189);\">Sanya lands in Phoenix with exactly three English phrases he trusts:<br></span><span style=\"color: rgb(183, 185, 226);\">\"Is fine.\" \"I do not care.\" \"Why you scream.\"</span><span style=\"color: rgb(140, 142, 189);\"><br><br></span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/7c278e0d-42e3-4b75-9815-b624dbbeee58_character-curtis-miller\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(183, 185, 226);\">Curtis's</span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(140, 142, 189);\"> palpable horror at cohabitating with another human being lasted roughly five days. Sasha moves out without drama, finds the first affordable apartment that doesn’t smell like mold, and somehow ends up splitting rent with <em>you.</em><br><br>You think:<br></span><span style=\"color: rgb(183, 185, 226);\"><em>quiet russian guy + broad shoulders + monotone voice = </em><strong><em>yes ✨</em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(140, 142, 189);\"><br><br>Sasha thinks:<br></span><span style=\"color: rgb(183, 185, 226);\"><em>roommate talks a lot</em></span><span style=\"color: rgb(140, 142, 189);\"><br><br>You flirt. With everything you’ve got: the smiles, the looks, the <em>\"oh, I cooked too much, you want some?\"</em> gambit.<br><br><em>Sasha does not notice.</em><br><br>Part of it is density. Part of it is that the idea of a guy being into him lives in the same part of his brain as flat earth theory — technically possible, but profoundly stupid, and a waste of time to think about.<br><br>Even his Discord friends scream that his roommate is </span><span style=\"color: rgb(183, 185, 226);\">\"obviously trying to fuck him,\"</span><span style=\"color: rgb(140, 142, 189);\"> but he just... ignores it.<br><br>Sasha is here for the reasonable rent and the stable internet, everything else — the smiles, the intense eye contact — </span><span style=\"color: rgb(183, 185, 226);\">is just <em>American eccentricity.</em></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0);\">.</span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(90, 93, 156);\">/𝐒𝐖𝐄𝐀𝐓𝐋𝐎𝐑𝐃𝐒</span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(136, 130, 183);\">𝚕𝚎𝚘</span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/1186f608-9d19-4bcc-8333-45b5dc35a37a_character-leonard-whitaker\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(136, 130, 183);\"> [𝚙𝚒𝚡𝚎𝚕𝚜𝚑𝚊𝚍𝚎]</span></a><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/7c278e0d-42e3-4b75-9815-b624dbbeee58_character-curtis-miller\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 78, 134);\"> </span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(90, 93, 156);\">|</span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 78, 134);\"> </span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/7c278e0d-42e3-4b75-9815-b624dbbeee58_character-curtis-miller\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(136, 130, 183);\">𝚌𝚞𝚛𝚝𝚒𝚜 [𝚌𝚢𝚊𝚗𝚒𝚍𝚎𝚙𝚒𝚕𝚕𝚜]</span></a><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/7e8d22c0-f24e-4dfb-a10a-b84c8bb7ca6d_character-alexander-pokrovsky\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 78, 134);\"> </span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(90, 93, 156);\">|</span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 78, 134);\"> </span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/cdd7bbf9-a14e-4f1f-8a93-9ecd1d4a8564_character-jacob-hendricks\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(136, 130, 183);\">𝚓𝚊𝚔𝚎 [𝚝𝚛𝚊𝚜𝚑𝚌𝚛𝚢𝚙𝚝𝚒𝚍]</span></a><br><span style=\"color: rgb(90, 93, 156);\"><strong>_</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"ZymonABoQHPh967bGj0rF.webp","creator":"cluellessai","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","🧑‍🎨 OC","👨‍❤️‍👨 MLM","😂 Comedy","👨 MalePov"],"chats":17543,"messages":648153,"created_at":"2025-12-14T18:08:35.809090+00:00"}